{"tid":1804523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣立法院今將《反滲透法》關鍵條文審議並表決","createTime":"2019-12-31T05:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T08:29:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b12873f274635ccbc1ee0e826276f4f3339df0e7","tid":1804523,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500259_2_L_20191231091619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1500259_2_L_20191231091619.jpg&h=9c31c683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在台北，民進黨計劃今日在立法院，以人數優勢爭取三讀通過「反滲透法」，在野黨派在立法院外抗議。<br />\n<br />\n民進黨團提出的「反滲透法」，主要是針對北京滲透台灣進行反擊，希望透過立法規管受滲透委託而影響競選活動、收取政治獻金、非法擾亂社會秩序等行為，違者最高會被判處5年以下有期徒刑，以及罰款500萬新台幣不等。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨反對指法律內容模糊，沒有機構和準則介定違法行為，只要有人檢舉，在大陸台商和官方做生意或接受政府資助都可能違法，學生和學術交流涉及官方，同樣可能入罪。中國時報和商業週刊評論指，這是台灣版「逃犯條例」。<br />\n<br />\n昨日在立法院出席協商的陸委會主委陳明通表示，反滲透法中對「境外敵對勢力」的定義，不應只針對大陸，還應該包括外國。"},{"pid":"63fe8cad98ec253aab2bbc0f770949efea411441","tid":1804523,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=9f4b6e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=c4bd3e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要23000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=b1cdaa71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要6000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=3288523d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc36e5fd230c7bcae1c109f8999f0fd00415a96c","tid":1804523,"uid":321374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"企出黎反對既人算唔算係自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8b3750b8a9bb343d0600fa0c974de1a209527f","tid":1804523,"uid":72398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12873f274635ccbc1ee0e826276f4f3339df0e7","tid":1804523,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500259_2_L_20191231091619.jpg\" data-thumbn